{"tid":1394793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拒絕分化]休息不可恥而且很有用","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T09:09:42.000Z","uid":130981,"like":122,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce97cda3980d0e67a29c9f16b82cf8ed7a8c36a","tid":1394793,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"發現身邊好多人都開始變返港豬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386996\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386996</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住日本社運當年點失敗<br />\n就係過程強調苦行<br />\n不斷切割<br />\n攻擊所有唔夠純粹唔夠虔誠嘅同行者<br />\n所以慢慢就越來越少人<br />\n被政府同媒體標籤<br />\n令到日本社運永不翻身<br />\n<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割𥱊</span></span>！<br />\n個個人承受壓力嘅能力都唔同<br />\n學d港女話齋 休息是為了走更長嘅路<br />\n休息同放鬆一d都唔可恥<br />\n好似象筋咁 一味扯到行只會好快就斷<br />\n得閒比自己放鬆下 吸下貓<br />\n我地打緊嘅係持久戰<br />\n<br />\n只要支持五大訴求嘅就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己人</span></span><br />\n休息夠就好出返嚟並肩作戰喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地等你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa99ce44ce3b603903786ca8b998469fcba2a8ea","tid":1394793,"uid":273803,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:11:08.000Z","msg":"認同。我覺得呢場仗，只少要打到十月"},{"pid":"c52e7b797dd4333547e8d5e1364c194196d649a1","tid":1394793,"uid":277873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"老土BUT TRUE<br />\n休息是為了走更遠<br />\n唔好死鬥長命<br />\n保養身體！"},{"pid":"573425b2b4ae338eb7fccf3065061a2f19cc383f","tid":1394793,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"66240121b00e27b12b0cc9b3d4c609a0d9626170","tid":1394793,"uid":39840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse